B

BaggedLOF - Class in weka.filters.unsupervised.attribute
A filter that applies the Bagged LOF (Local Outlier Factor) algorithm to compute an "outlier" score for each instance in the data.The filter appends to the input data a new attribute called "BaggedLOF".

For more information, see:

Aleksandar Lazarevic, Vipin Kumar: Feature Bagging for Outlier Detection.
